title: Buffalo Wild Wings 2 with Leslie Lee III
itunes:title: Buffalo Wild Wings 2 with Leslie Lee III
description:
Leslie Lee III (Struggle Session) joins the 'boys to talk about Keto in quarantine, food in Japan, and to revisit Buffalo Wild Wings. Plus, a Star Wars edition of Slop Quiz.
